HerdotagenowIdobegintopity:
For,meetingheroflatebehindthewood,
Seekingsweetfavoursfromthishatefulfool,
Ididupbraidherandfalloutwithher;
Forshehishairytemplesthenhadrounded
Withacoronetoffreshandfragrantflowers;
Andthatsamedew,whichsometimeonthebuds
Waswonttoswelllikeroundandorientpearls,
Stoodnowwithintheprettyflowerets'eyes
Liketearsthatdidtheirowndisgracebewail.
WhenIhadatmypleasuretauntedher
Andsheinmildtermsbegg'dmypatience,
Ithendidaskofherherchangelingchild;
Whichstraightshegaveme,andherfairysent
Tobearhimtomybowerinfairyland.
